Source: giflib
Section: libs
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Daniel Baumann <daniel@debian.org>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 5), autotools-dev
Standards-Version: 3.7.2

Package: giflib-dbg
Section: libdevel
Priority: extra
Architecture: any
Depends: giflib-tools (= ${Source-Version}), libgif4 (= ${Source-Version}), libgif-dev (= ${Source-Version})
Description: library for GIF images (debug)
 GIFLIB is a package of portable tools and library routines for working with GIF
 images.
 .
 This package contains the debugging symbols.

Package: giflib-tools
Section: utils
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}
Conflicts: giflib-bin, libungif-bin
Replaces: giflib-bin, libungif-bin
Description: library for GIF images (utilities)
 GIFLIB is a package of portable tools and library routines for working with GIF
 images.
 .
 This package contains additional utilities.

Package: libgif4
Section: libs
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}
Conflicts: giflib3g, libungif4g
Replaces: giflib3g, libungif4g
Description: library for GIF images (library)
 GIFLIB is a package of portable tools and library routines for working with GIF
 images.
 .
 This package contains the library.

Package: libgif-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: libgif4 (= ${Source-Version})
